original: FRENNE, Nils Gustaf Hezekiel, Direktör, Göteborg, f Hbg 10/4 89 av sadelm C Johansson o Ingrid Månsdtr, gm Maja Nyberg. Studex 08, KTH (mek) 12. Ing v Mell- o Norra Sv Ångpannefrn 13—16, v Ruthsaccumulator AB 17, övering 18, tekn dir 23, v. vkst dir 27—31, vkst dir AB Spontan 31—39, i Sv Flygmotor AB sed. 40, överflytt t Gbg f att där omhänderha AB:s ekon aff 43. Led av ing.frn i London samt Verein Deutsch Ing.
translated: FRENNE, Nils Gustaf Hezekiel, Director, Gothenburg, born in Helsingborg on April 10th, 1889, the son of saddle maker C Johansson and Ingrid Månsdtr, married to Maja Nyberg. Graduated from high school in 1908, KTH (Mechanical Engineering) in 1912. Employed at Mell- and Norra Sv Ångpannefrn from 1913 to 1916, Ruthsaccumulator AB in 1917, promoted in 1918, Technical Director in 1923, Vice Managing Director from 1927 to 1931, Managing Director of AB Spontan from 1931 to 1939, and employed at Sv Flygmotor AB since 1940. Transferred to Gothenburg in 1943 to manage the company's financial affairs. Member of the Engineering Association in London and Verein Deutsch Ing. Please note that "gm" denotes the abbreviation for married and the years are not provided for those marriages.

structured.name: Nils Gustaf Hezekiel FRENNE
structured.description: Nils Gustaf Hezekiel FRENNE was a Swedish director born on April 10th, 1889, in Helsingborg. He was the son of saddle maker C Johansson and Ingrid Månsdtr. He was married to Maja Nyberg. He graduated from high school in 1908 and obtained a bachelor's degree in Mechanical Engineering from KTH in 1912. Nils Gustaf Hezekiel FRENNE worked for several organizations throughout his career, including Mell- and Norra Sv Ångpannefrn from 1913 to 1916, Ruthsaccumulator AB in 1917, AB Spontan from 1931 to 1939, and Sv Flygmotor AB since 1940. In 1943, he was transferred to Gothenburg to manage the financial affairs of the company. He was also a member of the Engineering Association in London and Verein Deutsch Ing.
